<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>私域圈子加入与需求发布指南</title>
    <style>
        /* 基础样式 */
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        /* 响应式容器 */
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0 10px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        /* 标题样式 */
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin: 15px 0 20px 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            word-break: break-word;
        }
        
        h2 {
            color: #2980b9;
            margin-top: 25px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
            padding-left: 10px;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
        
        h3 {
            color: #3498db;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        
        /* 步骤卡片 */
        .step {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .step-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .step-number {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin-right: 10px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .step-title {
            font-size: 17px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        /* 列表样式 */
        ol, ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        
        li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        /* 提示样式 */
        .tip {
            background-color: #e8f4fc;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
        
        /* 图片容器 */
        .image-container {
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .image-container img {
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            object-fit: contain;
            height: auto;
            max-height: 400px;
            width: auto;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: block;
        }
        
        #qrcode-image {
            object-position: center;
            max-height: 250px;
        }
        
        #publish-image, #tag-image {
            object-position: center;
            max-height: 300px;
        }
        
        .image-caption {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin-top: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        /* 注意事项和FAQ部分 */
        .note-section {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 25px;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        
        .note-section h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .faq-item {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .faq-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            padding-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .faq-question {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .faq-answer {
            margin-top: 5px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        /* 页脚 */
        footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding-top: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        /* 错误提示 */
        .img-error {
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        /* 醒目提示横幅 */
        .highlight-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db, #2ecc71);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
            100% { box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        }
        
        .free-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #e74c3c;
            color: white;
            padding: 3px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-left: 3px;
            font-size: 15px;
            animation: blink 1.5s infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes blink {
            0% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.7; }
            100% { opacity: 1; }
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 15px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 8px 10px;
            display: inline-block;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .contact-label {
            font-weight: normal;
            margin-right: 3px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        .contact-value {
            font-weight: bold;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-right: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        /* 全屏图片查看 */
        .fullscreen-img {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
            display: none;
            z-index: 1000;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            touch-action: none;
        }
        
        .fullscreen-img img {
            max-width: 90%;
            max-height: 90%;
            object-fit: contain;
        }
        
        .close-fullscreen {
            position: absolute;
            top: 15px;
            right: 15px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            z-index: 1001;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        
        /* 点击放大提示 */
        .zoom-hint {
            position: absolute;
            right: 10px;
            top: 10px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 12px;
            opacity: 0.7;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        /* 移动端优化 */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
                font-size: 15px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }
            
            .step {
                padding: 12px;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }
            
            .step-title {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
            
            .contact-info {
                display: flex;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
            }
            
            .highlight-banner {
                padding: 12px 10px;
                font-size: 15px;
            }
            
            .free-tag {
                margin-top: 3px;
            }
            
            .contact-info {
                font-size: 14px;
                padding: 6px 8px;
            }
            
            ol, ul {
                padding-left: 18px;
            }
            
            .image-container {
                margin: 15px 0;
            }
            
            /* 增强移动端的触摸操作体验 */
            .zoom-hint {
                padding: 4px 6px;
                font-size: 11px;
            }
            
            .note-section {
                padding: 12px;
            }
            
            .faq-item {
                margin-bottom: 12px;
                padding-bottom: 12px;
            }
        }
        
        /* 小屏手机优化 */
        @media (max-width: 380px) {
            body {
                padding: 8px;
                font-size: 14px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }
            
            .step-number {
                width: 24px;
                height: 24px;
                font-size: 12px;
            }
            
            .step-title {
                font-size: 15px;
            }
            
            .contact-value, .contact-label {
                font-size: 13px;
                margin-bottom: 3px;
            }
        }
        
        /* 点击态效果，增强移动端操作反馈 */
        .image-container img {
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        
        .image-container img:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
        }
        
        /* 移动优化：防止过度缩放 */
        .pinch-zoom-container {
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        /* 自动隐藏放大提示 */
        @media (any-hover: none) {
            .zoom-hint {
                opacity: 1;
                animation: fadeOut 3s forwards;
                animation-delay: 2s;
            }
            
            @keyframes fadeOut {
                to { opacity: 0; }
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>私域圈子加入与需求发布指南</h1>
        
        <div class="highlight-banner">
            特别提醒：直播间、渠道可以<span class="free-tag">免费加入</span>，无需任何费用！
            <div class="contact-info">
                <span class="contact-label">联系人：</span>
                <span class="contact-value">骆姐</span>
                <span class="contact-label">微信号：</span>
                <span class="contact-value">iamxiaoluo</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 全屏图片查看器 -->
        <div class="fullscreen-img" id="fullscreen-view">
            <span class="close-fullscreen" onclick="closeFullscreen()">&times;</span>
            <div class="pinch-zoom-container">
                <img src="" id="fullscreen-image" alt="放大查看">
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step">
            <div class="step-header">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <h3 class="step-title">扫码加入私域圈子</h3>
            </div>
            <ol>
                <li>打开您的微信应用</li>
                <li>点击右上角的"+"图标，选择"扫一扫"功能</li>
                <li>对准我们提供的二维码进行扫描</li>
                <li>根据提示完成添加好友或关注公众号的操作</li>
                <li>等待审核通过（如果有审核环节）</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="image-container">
                <div class="zoom-hint">点击查看大图</div>
                <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="扫码加入私域圈子" id="qrcode-image" onclick="showFullscreen(this)">
                <div class="image-caption">扫描上方二维码加入私域圈子</div>
                <div class="img-error" id="qrcode-error" style="display: none;">图片加载失败</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <strong>提示：</strong>请确保您的微信版本为最新版本，以避免扫码过程中出现问题。
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step">
            <div class="step-header">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <h3 class="step-title">进入圈子并发布动态</h3>
            </div>
            <ol>
                <li>成功加入私域圈子后，打开相关群聊或社区页面</li>
                <li>找到页面底部或顶部的"发布"按钮</li>
                <li>点击"发布动态"选项</li>
